---
title: Salmon Limone with Zesty Quinoa Salad
description: Salmon fillets are coated in our Italian Seasoning, then seared to golden perfection and a lovely lemon crema is spooned over top. A bright quinoa salad with fresh tomatoes and zucchini make this a delightfully light affair.

